Reasoning: The paper presents a new 3D shape retrieval system that allows users to explore 3D shape and image collections by reasoning about objects at the level of their constituent parts. This involves techniques from computer vision (cs.CV) for image analysis and retrieval, computer graphics (cs.GR) for 3D shape representation and manipulation, multimedia (cs.MM) for handling image and shape collections, artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for formulating advanced search queries, and machine learning (cs.LG) for developing models to support the retrieval system.
